> <PERSON> Hendrix </PERSON>, dead, 1970 drug overdose; `` _ <PERSON> Keith </PERSON> <PERSON> Moon </PERSON> of the Who, dead of a drug overdose in'78; `` _ <ORGANIZATION> Paul </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Butterfield </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Blues </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Band </ORGANIZATION> _ <PERSON> Butterfield </PERSON> died of a drug `` <LOCATION> Woodstock </LOCATION> was a time of a great deal of tolerance for drug use and it was also a time of a great deal of death, because of the tolerance of drugs,'' said <PERSON> Bennett </PERSON>.
